%% Bi / Group 2 / Path 2
%% Admission and disposition path - production-ready network
flowchart LR

  subgraph LEGEND["How to Read This Graph"]
    LG1["Square node = active promoted ingress-truth boundary or owned closure"]
    LG2[("Round node = durable ingress truth / evidence surface")]
    LG3["This graph closes at ingress-owned disposition truth, before authoritative bus publication begins"]
  end

  ENTRY["Boundary-valid request<br/>correct front door / route / auth already satisfied"]

  subgraph PATH["Bi / Group 2 / Path 2 - Admission and disposition"]
    IGLAMBDA["Ingress Lambda handler<br/>owned admission / disposition boundary"]
    DEDUPE["Deterministic ingress basis<br/>platform_run_id / event_class / event_id<br/>duplicate-safe identity + TTL"]
    HEALTH["Truthful fail-closed health semantics<br/>local sickness separated from neighboring contention"]
    IGDDB[("Durable ingress idempotency + admission truth")]
    RECEIPTS[("Receipt / quarantine evidence surface")]
    QUAR[("Quarantine truth")]
    OUT[("Owned outcome<br/>production-ready ingress-owned disposition truth")]
  end

  ENTRY -->|hands valid request to| IGLAMBDA
  IGLAMBDA -->|computes canonical disposition basis in| DEDUPE
  DEDUPE -->|is judged through| HEALTH
  HEALTH -->|writes durable ingress truth to| IGDDB
  IGLAMBDA -->|emits receipt and quarantine refs to| RECEIPTS
  RECEIPTS -->|closes quarantine evidence in| QUAR
  IGDDB -->|commits admitted / duplicate-safe / invalid-reject / retry-governed truth as| OUT
  QUAR -->|contributes quarantined truth to| OUT
